<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Loop paused — out of credits</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#FAFAF7;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;color:#1A1A1A;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background:#FAFAF7;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding:32px 16px;">
        <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:600px;width:100%;background:#FFFFFF;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:40px 32px 16px 32px;">
              <h1 style="margin:0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;font-size:26px;line-height:1.3;color:#1A1A1A;">
                {% if first_name %}{{ first_name }} — your Loop paused.{% else %}Your Loop paused.{% endif %}
              </h1>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px 32px 24px 32px;">
              <p style="margin:0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.55;color:#1A1A1A;">
                <span style="font-weight:700;">{{ loop_name }}</span> ran out of credits for this month. It'll resume on its own when your next month's credits land.
              </p>
              <p style="margin:14px 0 0 0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.55;color:#1A1A1A;">
                If you want it running sooner, you can upgrade your plan.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px 32px 32px 32px;">
              <a href="{{ fleet_url }}" style="display:inline-block;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:14px;color:#1A1A1A;text-decoration:underline;margin-right:18px;">View your Loops &rarr;</a>
              <a href="{{ upgrade_url }}" style="display:inline-block;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:14px;color:#1A1A1A;text-decoration:underline;">Upgrade &rarr;</a>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:32px 32px 40px 32px;border-top:1px solid #E5E5E5;">
              <div style="font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:#1A1A1A;">
                — Sid
              </div>
              <div style="margin-top:18px;font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#888888;">
                Offerloop &middot; Not Forwarded.
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
